{"tid":165374,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想領養貓仔","createTime":"2017-03-21T10:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T09:24:56.000Z","uid":40652,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3561dc468db4a2f686c0732411448afe801594b5","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"戴左頭盔先...未實行...仲係討論緊<br />\n<br />\n屋企花園附近有好多老鼠...想養兩隻貓黎治鼠...<br />\n但有個好嚴重既問題...兩隻貓唔準入屋...但會整貓屋比佢地住...會定時餵貓糧...<br />\n<br />\n咁樣養會唔會好衰...唔好屌住...聽完意見先決定..."},{"pid":"ccfc423c61b67f41591123ba5b6ca363b0cee2f2","tid":165374,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"就算我冇養貓我都覺得你咁做係好仆街"},{"pid":"1c80a23fcfbe5981b6de281f4d345a81e05f29e7","tid":165374,"uid":80764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戴左頭盔先...未實行...仲係討論緊<br />\n<br />\n屋企花園附近有好多老鼠...想養兩隻貓黎治鼠...<br />\n但有個好嚴重既問題...兩隻貓唔準入屋...但會整貓屋比佢地住...會定時餵貓糧...<br />\n<br />\n咁樣養會唔會好衰...唔好屌住...聽完意見先決定...</blockquote><br />\n咁鄉下嘅你諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n滅蟲公司聽過未？"},{"pid":"6b6ee6f0035b8bbb40fee1461a3c581a6a061cf8","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算我冇養貓我都覺得你咁做係好仆街</blockquote><br />\n未實行，諗緊會唔會好仆街<br />\n我住圍村，以前我媽係外面收到個消息，有廿幾隻貓無人領養就拎去人道，最後我媽拎哂返黎係圍村放生...最後條村好多貓四圍走好開心<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗，咁樣養係咪真係好仆街"},{"pid":"ff235355e5d9c70bb3a9097862d1d091a4e724b2","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戴左頭盔先...未實行...仲係討論緊<br />\n<br />\n屋企花園附近有好多老鼠...想養兩隻貓黎治鼠...<br />\n但有個好嚴重既問題...兩隻貓唔準入屋...但會整貓屋比佢地住...會定時餵貓糧...<br />\n<br />\n咁樣養會唔會好衰...唔好屌住...聽完意見先決定...</blockquote><br />\n咁鄉下嘅你諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n滅蟲公司聽過未？</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得滅蟲公司用既化學品好破壞環境"},{"pid":"6dbc34ce545e99d29b6ff9ff8387c8003a1bbd4a","tid":165374,"uid":57110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79130e76ccd406e1a3e5c21a8280839100d89e5a","tid":165374,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>戴左頭盔先...未實行...仲係討論緊<br />\n<br />\n屋企花園附近有好多老鼠...想養兩隻貓黎治鼠...<br />\n但有個好嚴重既問題...兩隻貓唔準入屋...但會整貓屋比佢地住...會定時餵貓糧...<br />\n<br />\n咁樣養會唔會好衰...唔好屌住...聽完意見先決定...</blockquote><br />\n咁鄉下嘅你諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n滅蟲公司聽過未？</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得滅蟲公司用既化學品好破壞環境</blockquote><br />\n你邊到黎個想法覺得有貓一定無老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29ae45856ebdb48e2a68c4a5e692fe588a78799","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁養狗？"},{"pid":"5d1f7c763edfcac665d99d5ed9f15ac16d7ca08c","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>戴左頭盔先...未實行...仲係討論緊<br />\n<br />\n屋企花園附近有好多老鼠...想養兩隻貓黎治鼠...<br />\n但有個好嚴重既問題...兩隻貓唔準入屋...但會整貓屋比佢地住...會定時餵貓糧...<br />\n<br />\n咁樣養會唔會好衰...唔好屌住...聽完意見先決定...</blockquote><br />\n咁鄉下嘅你諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n滅蟲公司聽過未？</blockquote><br />\n我成日覺得滅蟲公司用既化學品好破壞環境</blockquote><br />\n你邊到黎個想法覺得有貓一定無老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前屋企都有隻自來黑貓...果排真係無老鼠...但最後隻貓又自己走左"},{"pid":"fe9cd2489b630b82227188249e4128ba8b625d2d","tid":165374,"uid":57110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁養狗？</blockquote><br />\n貓狗會當老鼠係玩具。<br />\n但係唔係隻隻都鐘意玩玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"666f18df369feff03a30961118483dcffe8fe798","tid":165374,"uid":75522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁養狗？</blockquote><br />\n住村<br />\n以前養左隻唐狗識捉(玩)老鼠<br />\n但有一次佢玩緊個陣俾隻老鼠咬左個鼻一野<br />\n從此怕老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55641a6672674d444d27bf289e5323a54026a371","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁養狗？</blockquote><br />\n住村<br />\n以前養左隻唐狗識捉(玩)老鼠<br />\n但有一次佢玩緊個陣俾隻老鼠咬左個鼻一野<br />\n從此怕老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前做D細車房...日日返到去都見到D車房狗殺鼠"},{"pid":"878f06966a9966584c9ac209e3a77c5cbb7827eb","tid":165374,"uid":28167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>貓唔一定會治鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁養狗？</blockquote><br />\n住村<br />\n以前養左隻唐狗識捉(玩)老鼠<br />\n但有一次佢玩緊個陣俾隻老鼠咬左個鼻一野<br />\n從此怕老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渣ga"},{"pid":"bc77e75d96ea3c49164011a2c88c3e8f609a6f94","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"無結果？"},{"pid":"7de5de6393ae44190bd1c1af71bea480dfb28a8b","tid":165374,"uid":60721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無結果？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果兩隻貓最後冇幫你捉老鼠，你會唔會唔要?"},{"pid":"f5cdb69bbe7885efda3e052ff4b0273ac56afad6","tid":165374,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:39:06.000Z","msg":"咪撚害隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f27871027be444ac3ca93f2f86c76fb2ca4d089","tid":165374,"uid":48946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:42:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦 當工具？<br />\n有病你肯撚定唔會醫<br />\n定期餵糧好威威豬啵<br />\n咪撚害佢地"},{"pid":"f292b047081739eacf4e225a24c5cba5d4330546","tid":165374,"uid":55391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:44:55.000Z","msg":"捉唔捉老鼠其實好難講<br />\n貓都有勤力有懶<br />\n有d會同老鼠一齊share嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96acb192d7e4b22ee3bfd195b3225a308c8b2652","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母啦 當工具？<br />\n有病你肯撚定唔會醫<br />\n定期餵糧好威威豬啵<br />\n咪撚害佢地</blockquote><br />\n你含柒啦<br />\n你話肯定唔會醫？<br />\n我本身有養開家貓<br />\n個撚個好似你咁撚狗咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"51fc781a50c75b23131aecb6c8703b26ac5a450f","tid":165374,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無結果？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果兩隻貓最後冇幫你捉老鼠，你會唔會唔要?</blockquote><br />\n唔會"},{"pid":"1c1f4daaf27f1f4ba3125671ec47701822e5d3d7","tid":165374,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"仆街喇你"},{"pid":"53185e2a7a135587dbb9f4602b3ac21818c8d46f","tid":165374,"uid":52597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"唔覺有咩問題 當放養囉 如果有人肯借隻貓畀你捉老鼠就更加好 唔駛養添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a45306104539d9bae4e4b382123b8d4df75bb46","tid":165374,"uid":74738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"點解唔比入屋?"},{"pid":"3d96011dc2bc4b1f64a2faaa80ef0a01de72efc5","tid":165374,"uid":60721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無結果？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果兩隻貓最後冇幫你捉老鼠，你會唔會唔要?</blockquote><br />\n唔會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我又覺得冇咩問題，依家其實好多圍村人，鋪頭都係放養形式去養貓，最緊要係你唔會因為佢地捉唔到老鼠而忽略對佢地既愛護，不過戶外養貓真係要多加小心，分分鐘佢地話走就走，要注意"},{"pid":"5ce74e8decc5497827f364246f141b7c39a14455","tid":165374,"uid":60721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"總之唔理你咩原因而養貓啦，最緊要決定左就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好棄養</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}